# ==============================================
# CONNECTION TYPES BY PORT
# ==============================================
# Port 22    = SSH (ZTE, Huawei, Nokia)
# Port 23    = Telnet (VSOL, DBC, CDATA, ECOM, BDCOM, Fiberhome)
# Port 80    = HTTP API
# Port 443   = HTTPS API
# Port 8041, 8080 = HTTP API
# Custom ports = Auto-detect based on brand
#
# ==============================================
# SUPPORTED OLT BRANDS & DEFAULT PROTOCOLS
# ==============================================
# ZTE       - SSH port 22
# Huawei    - SSH port 22
# Nokia     - SSH port 22
# VSOL      - Telnet port 23 (or custom like 8085)
# DBC       - Telnet port 23 (or custom)
# CDATA     - Telnet port 23 (or custom)
# ECOM      - Telnet port 23 (or custom)
# BDCOM     - Telnet port 23 (or custom)
# Fiberhome - Telnet port 23
